113 g Lentils
340 g Sweet Potato, cubes
1 tsp Italian Seasoning
1 tbsp Honey
227 g Brussels Sprouts
113 g Onion, chopped
1 unit Vegetable Broth Concentrate
2 tbsp Balsamic Vinegar
28 g Pepitas
56 g Feta Cheese, crumbled
